## Introduction to `gtsummary`

Next, we'll use the `gtsummary` package, an extension of the `gt` table formatting package, that can incorporate statistical model outputs into publication-ready tables.

## Descriptive statistics

The base R approach to getting summary statistics for a dataframe results in a thorough, but not well-formatted for publication, table.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
summary(smartpill)
```

